{"tid":2160782,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白俄反對派領袖稱準備領導國家　促保安部隊「變節」 　揚言會原諒他們","createTime":"2020-08-17T07:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T10:25:05.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"baace12b053c32f7ba054fbc0f211cd0e2e8b76d","tid":2160782,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:39:10.000Z","msg":"示威者要求總統盧卡申科辭職，又促請當局釋放政治犯。<br />\n<br />\n參選總統落敗的反對派候選人季哈諾夫斯卡婭表示，準備領導國家，呼籲建立法律機制，以確保再次舉行公正的總統選舉。<br />\n<br />\n身在立陶宛季哈諾夫斯卡婭發表錄影講話，敦促安全和執法人員「變節」，揚言會原諒他們過去所犯的罪行。<br />\n<br />\n而盧卡申科在親政府集會上形容反對派是鼠輩，又關注北約即將在波蘭及立陶宛的軍事演習，大肆抨擊西方的軍事聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n另外，盧卡申科連續第二日同俄羅斯總統普京通電話，普京重申確保白俄羅斯安全。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544152-20200817.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544152-20200817.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRg9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=7fdc2ebe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544152-20200817.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=51f7ed5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544152-20200817.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4373d50f34a08532f99cbed93b797e8cc70d8492","tid":2160782,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:39:50.000Z","msg":"識玩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f048d7208d19ae91b7743ee3fefae6b007c5d3ca","tid":2160782,"uid":37058,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"但係佢第一時間走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />白羅斯人服唔服佢"},{"pid":"0dd812729b070efbb0850ced4b95a369c494e66e","tid":2160782,"uid":34869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:42:27.000Z","msg":"呢單同克利米亞有少少唔同<br />\n選前民調呢個女人真係有8成支持度<br />\n<br />\n而克利米亞係一早被殖民以為自己係俄羅斯人"},{"pid":"16b7d1e4539fd5c4d